text: Cycle is an unincorporated community in Yadkin County, North Carolina. ==History== A post office called Cycle was established in 1904, and remained in operation until 1972. The origin of the name "Cycle" is obscure. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Yadkin County, North Carolina Category:Unincorporated communities in North Carolina
title: Cycle, North Carolina
